        "text": "2Chronicles 13:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".) Hence the phrases used by the Greeks to denote the breach of a covenant, “Where is the salt?” and “They overstepped the salt.” (Comp. Pliny, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
