        "text": ", all the holy gifts enumerated in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Numbers 18:9-18",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Jehovah gives these to the priests as an eternal claim. \"An eternal covenant of salt is this before Jehovah,\" for Aaron and his descendants. A \"covenant of salt;\" equivalent to an indissoluble covenant, or inviolable contract (see at ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Leviticus 2:13",
